name: Sky Flyer II
overview: A sequel to the original Sky Flyer game, like the original this is a PD\Freeware game based on the SEUCK engine created by Andrew Fez Fereday. It features Aerial combat in a late WW1 setting where you need to take out enemy planes, ground emplacements and tanks all of which are trying to blast you out of the skies.
